msgid "Jumpers lose platforms.{{BR}}Don't be a jumper."
msgstr "Hyppelijät kadottavat{{BR}}alustoja.{{BR}}Älä ole hyppelijä."

#. Part of 'Try going in circles, but five is right out!'
#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8097]
msgid "Try going in circles, but ..."
msgstr "Yritä kulkea ympyröitä, mutta..."

#. Part of 'Try going in circles, but five is right out!' (Monty Python
#. reference, i.e. 'right out' in the sense of 'out of the question', 'not an
#. option')
#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8104]
msgid "... five is right out!"
msgstr "...viisi ei tule kysymykseen!"

#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8114]
msgid "Mwahaha!"
msgstr "Muahaha!"

#. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N78CavWrtjw - try to be somewhat consistent
#. with some existing translation if you can find one, but also try making
#. sure the word for 'space' can have both the geometrical and the
#. astronomical meaning
#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8235]
msgid ""
"Let's put weird and weird together,{{BR}}and make it even "
"weirder!{{BR}}Weird, weird space{{BR}}is super-weird!{{BR}}{{BR}}Press "
"{{ExitButton}}."
msgstr ""
"Laitetaan outo ja outo yhteen,{{BR}}ja tehdään siitä vielä "
"oudompaa!{{BR}}Outo, outo avaruus{{BR}}on superoutoa!{{BR}}{{BR}}Paina "
"{{ExitButton}}."

#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8246]
msgid "4 ..."
msgstr "4..."

#: assets/maps/level.tmx//map/objectgroup/object[@id=8247]
msgid "5 ..."
msgstr "5..."

